User -> UI: Enter password
UI -> SaltGen: Request salt generation
SaltGen -> SaltGen: Generate cryptographic random salt
SaltGen -> UI: Return unique salt
UI -> Hasher: Hash password with salt
Hasher -> Hasher: Combine password + salt
Hasher -> Hasher: Apply SHA-256 hashing
Hasher -> UI: Return hash digest
UI -> DB: Store hash + salt
DB -> UI: Confirm storage
UI -> User: Registration successful